  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring the glass to the customer!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As two construction workers, you are transporting a glass window for a tall structure. On this journey you have to be careful with the glass because it is very fragile. Can you make it to the top without breaking it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer: Get help from a friend to carry the glass!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite a trusted friend to your lobby to carry the glass with you!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=644 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters with physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've added physics to every part of the characters to improve the gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=592 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skyscraper & Lighthouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/7a30ab97afe5e35ab5ff96c176b2d795.avif?t=1771068318\" width=899 height=404 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes: Normal, Hard (less checkpoints), Impossible (no checkpoints)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want a more casual experience, you should try Normal mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But if you believe you can make it to the top without breaking the glass, then hard mode or the impossible mode might be for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/63f862ef75ff5c867170d730e7acb30f.avif?t=1771068318\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras_big/63f862ef75ff5c867170d730e7acb30f.avif?t=1771068318 width=800 height=274 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring the glass to the customer!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As two construction workers, you are transporting a glass window for a tall structure. On this journey you have to be careful with the glass because it is very fragile. Can you make it to the top without breaking it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/437cf12a3def76670a6f953f749ef3ee.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer: Get help from a friend to carry the glass!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite a trusted friend to your lobby to carry the glass with you!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=644 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/3c2e1e12d1c9e2d3512db830f70d6be6.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters with physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We've added physics to every part of the characters to improve the gameplay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.poster.avif?t=1771068318\" width=592 height=514 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.webm?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/4051855d294fa5f781f39411ce2e189c.mp4?t=1771068318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skyscraper & Lighthouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/7a30ab97afe5e35ab5ff96c176b2d795.avif?t=1771068318\" width=899 height=404 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes: Normal, Hard (less checkpoints), Impossible (no checkpoints)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want a more casual experience, you should try Normal mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But if you believe you can make it to the top without breaking the glass, then hard mode or the impossible mode might be for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras/63f862ef75ff5c867170d730e7acb30f.avif?t=1771068318\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263320/extras_big/63f862ef75ff5c867170d730e7acb30f.avif?t=1771068318 width=800 height=274 /></span></p>",
